# shadcn/ui CLI - Latest Commands & Best Practices

## ‚ö†Ô∏è Important: Use Latest CLI Package

**ALWAYS use `npx shadcn@latest`** - the old `shadcn-ui` package is deprecated.

## üöÄ Core Commands

### Initialize Project

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

**Options:**

- `--defaults` - Use default values (New York style, Zinc color, CSS variables)
- `--force` - Force overwrite existing [components.json](mdc:components.json)
- `--yes` - Skip confirmation prompts
- `--cwd <path>` - Specify working directory

### Add Components

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]
```

**Options:**

- `--yes` - Skip confirmation prompts
- `--overwrite` - Overwrite existing files
- `--cwd <path>` - Specify working directory
- `--path <path>` - Specify component path

## üìù Common Usage Examples

```bash
# Quick setup with defaults
npx shadcn@latest init --defaults --yes

# Add single component
npx shadcn@latest add button

# Add multiple components
npx shadcn@latest add button checkbox dialog sheet

# Add component with overwrite (useful for updates)
npx shadcn@latest add button --overwrite --yes

# Add all common UI components at once
npx shadcn@latest add accordion alert alert-dialog avatar badge breadcrumb button calendar card carousel checkbox collapsible command context-menu dialog dropdown-menu hover-card input label menubar navigation-menu popover progress radio-group scroll-area select separator sheet skeleton slider switch table tabs textarea toast toggle tooltip
```

## üéØ Project-Specific Notes

### For Astro + React + Tailwind CSS v4

- Components work with `client:load` directive
- Import path uses `@/components/ui/` (configured in [components.json](mdc:components.json))
- Tailwind CSS v4 setup in [src/styles/global.css](mdc:src/styles/global.css) is compatible
- Use semantic color classes: `bg-primary`, `text-primary-foreground`, etc.

### Component Integration Pattern

```tsx
// In .astro files
---
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
---

<Button client:load variant="outline">Click me</Button>
```

## üîß Troubleshooting

1. **Missing components.json**: Run `npx shadcn@latest init` first
2. **Import errors**: Check alias configuration in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
3. **Styling issues**: Ensure [src/styles/global.css](mdc:src/styles/global.css) includes Tailwind CSS imports
4. **React component errors**: Add `client:load` directive in Astro files

